---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

import { SITE } from "../site";
const siteTitle = SITE.title;
const tagline = SITE.description;

---
<BaseLayout title={siteTitle} description={tagline}>
 
 <main class="page-home">

  <section class="w-1-c">
    <img
    src="/images/W-0.png"
    alt="Joy Lemon Art header image"
    loading="eager"
  />
  <img src="/images/w-1-c.png" alt="Joy Lemon Art showcase" loading="eager" />
</section>

<section class="slideshow">
  <div class="slideshow-viewport">
    <img src="/images/P-1.png" alt="Joy Lemon Art 作品一" class="slide active" />
    <img src="/images/P-2.png" alt="Joy Lemon Art 作品二" class="slide" />
    <img src="/images/P-3.png" alt="Joy Lemon Art 作品三" class="slide" />
    <img src="/images/P-4.png" alt="Joy Lemon Art 作品四" class="slide" />
    <img src="/images/P-5.png" alt="Joy Lemon Art 作品五" class="slide" />
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.slide');
  let index = 0;

  setInterval(() => {
    slides[index].classList.remove('active');
    index = (index + 1) % slides.length;
    slides[index].classList.add('active');
  }, 5000); // 每 3 秒切换
</script>


  <section class="card">
    <h1>{siteTitle}</h1>
    <p class="small">{tagline}</p>
    <p>
      JOY LEMON ART STUDIO is a creative art space where children are encouraged to explore, imagine, and express their inner world through art. We believe every child is a natural artist, possessing a unique creative voice and endless imagination.
Created by artists for young artists, our studio offers a warm and inspiring environment that respects individuality and celebrates creativity. Through art exploration, children engage their senses, discover beauty, and express genuine feelings through color, form, and creative drawing.
At JOY LEMON ART STUDIO, we nurture creativity as a way of self-expression—helping children discover their talents and tell their own stories through art.
JOY LEMON ART STUDIO
    </p>
    <p>
    艺术空间旨在提供一个让孩子释放心灵光芒的艺术场所，坚信每个孩子都是一位天生的艺术家，拥有无限的创造力和想象力。
    我们尊重每个孩子的独特个性，珍视孩子独特的创造力，通过引导孩子们了解文化和艺术家的故事，激发他们的艺术创意和思维创造力。
    在这里，我们鼓励孩子运用感官去感受美，了解美、创造美，并通过艺术手法表达内心真实感受。我们强调孩子的创意和创造力的培养，引导他们用创意表现美、表现心灵，以及用创意绘画来表达自己内心深处的感受。
    我们鼓励他们在这个创意的空间里，发现自己的才华，用色彩和形状诉说属于他们的故事。
    </p>
    <p>
      <a class="button" href="/contact">Contact / Register</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  </div>
  </section>

  </main>
  
</BaseLayout>
